  "design_notes": "Easy chart designed to maintain an engaging but highly accessible step pattern. Focuses on comfortable quarter-note rhythms during high-energy drop sections, interspersed with holds to emphasize longer vocal or synth sustains. Breather sections utilize sparse steps on the main beats to ensure the player is never left standing still for more than 4 seconds. Crossovers and jacks are completely avoided to keep the movement natural and beginner-friendly.",
